cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.GR

The paper deals with transfer learning in reinforcement learning tasks using image-to-image translation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) since the paper heavily relies on image processing techniques. The paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO) since it deals with learning control policies. Finally, the paper involves graphics (cs.GR) since it uses visual variants of games to demonstrate the approach.
